This is a pathfinding visualizer implemented using Dijkstra's Algorithm.

Setup:

- Install requirements from the requirements.txt file
- Run `pathfinder.py` using the terminal or IDE of your choice

Rules:

- The starting position is the first cell (0, 0)
- Using the mouse, hold/press the left click button to create a wall
- Set destination by pressing the right mouse button
- To start the visualization, press any key on the keyboard

Citations:

- https://youtu.be/QNpUN8gBeLY?si=SdJU-9tFmKLj2fbc
- https://www.pygame.org/docs/
